headline: Q3 Earnings Highs And Lows: Analog Devices (NASDAQ:ADI) Vs The Rest Of The Analog Semiconductors Stocks
summary: Quarterly earnings results are a good time to check in on a company’s progress, especially compared to its peers in the same sector. Today we are looking at Analog Devices (NASDAQ:ADI) and the best and worst performers in the analog semiconductors industry.

headline: Beijing Pushes to Use China-Made Chips in Its EVs
summary: China wants the chips inside EVs to be Chinese-made, while the U.S. is objecting to the country’s push for self-sufficiency in the $80 billion business.
